{"tid":2190253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭若驊開腔：不少人談及「三權分立」，市民不應只著眼於一個概念的表面稱謂！","createTime":"2020-09-05T13:18:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T16:28:11.000Z","uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"42398172fcb23b19e527b746f442a2f929060081","tid":2190253,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T13:18:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n鄭若驊指香港行政主導　楊潤雄指教科書談政制按基本法<br />\n<br />\n律政司司長鄭若驊說，近日不少人談及「三權分立」，強調香港是「行政主導」，行政長官領導特區政府、決定政策，而司法獨立不受影響，市民不應只著眼於一個概念的表面稱謂。教育局局長楊潤雄重申，本港並非三權分立，又指中學教科書涉及基本知識，非政治討論，描述本港政制時應該按照《基本法》。<br />\n<br />\n2020-09-05 21:06:10<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548061-20200905.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548061-20200905.htm&d=bvaV6%2BUCrkGuzNdoarVmR9qeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=cdd198e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548061-20200905.htm&h=aec026d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548061-20200905.htm</a>"},{"pid":"610eede8bae623a25e260199156c1072abe39945","tid":2190253,"uid":199689,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T13:29:27.000Z","msg":"無人讚你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76fc3ca9781c3c56498a5c19067f0bc7d2a66264","tid":2190253,"uid":296830,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T13:50:47.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"large\">老共「七不講」（普世價值、新聞自由、公民社會、公民權利、中國共產黨的歷史錯誤、權貴資產階級，以及司法獨立，全部不要講）<br />\n宜家香港墜落，開始七不講，不講新聞自由、司法獨立</span></strong>"},{"pid":"4386f5b336f563b316e916c18c999eba446f5141","tid":2190253,"uid":61690,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T13:59:32.000Z","msg":"一個概念的表面稱謂<br />\n佢on99"},{"pid":"6fb1306dbb8c84ca6b80